Antagony jumped back when Perndabot landed near her. She aimed her acid 
launcher at him but didn't fire. Around the two bots, all the animals 
suddenly became quiet as if sensing the tension.

"I'm friendly." Antagony replied while eying Perndabot. He was almost twice 
her size, but she wasn't scared of him. Somehow, she knew that he wouldn't 
fire on her and would take her to his base. It was a talent she had, telling 
the future.
